Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:22.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}沿着地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:27.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}连接着天空和地球的云
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}团团围住我所在的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:35.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在一个半梦半醒慵懒的午后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}撕开棉花糖般的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:45.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在云彩对面朦胧可见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:53.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}凝眸远眺　看啊　那里有着通往夏天的小小入口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:59.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}蝉鸣如雨点般响个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}拼命追逐着的独角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:08.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}融掉的棒冰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:13.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回溯的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:17.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}再也回不到的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:23.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be5}却是永不磨灭的回忆
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸灯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就帮你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  你那边忙好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过难得来那么多客人  真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  在许愿板上要写什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 我还没决定好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  好好想一想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似还很灵验的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想啊野心什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名我呀～总而言之就是好想留学～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在外国学一些关于旅馆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有还有～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位娇小的女性神明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了报答用纸灯照亮她的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而把他们的愿望带到天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到汤乃鹭后  我希望自己能够闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后每天都过得手忙脚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得自己已经喜欢上工作和喜翠庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的梦想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数如此众多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到晚餐的筹备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够尽可能地削减花在早餐上的劳力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐不要送到客房  而是用自助餐的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想会有客人喜欢在房间里慢慢吃早饭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没法子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房已经忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人退房后打扫房间也很难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子她们还要去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再使用每个房间都由专人负责的形式了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在揽客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吩咐过你们不要再接待客人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是其他旅馆揽得更多都没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们这么多人不停叫唤着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还叫没事么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要降低服务的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要努力下一番工夫来克服眼前的困境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是自助餐  料理还是料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝没有半点想偷工减料的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管没有专门负责的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在其他所有方面上  我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  随你们喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有雪洞祭  你们得用以往的方式给我好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…这些是许愿板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…在上面写上各自的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在纸灯上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做那些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拿一块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样希望喜翠庄可以继续开下去但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你罢手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再站在老板娘那一边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是站哪一边什么的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能回的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回的…地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟雪洞祭什么的根本没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有…我的梦想在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为…本以为你跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还高兴过那么一阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在喜翠庄工作的所有人都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜… 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里住上一阵  没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但睡那地方没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天实在是忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想多出一点力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在努力…大家虽然都在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不觉得大家有在雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  与其要睡那边的话  不如到我床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  快点睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天四点就要起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在都已经过了十二点了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得小菜也在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却连聊天都不能聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太沉闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子…实在有点…讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可没工夫悠悠哉哉地散步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要帮忙的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你在大家面前说句话的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在老板娘那边也只会被大家孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是站哪一边的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想让喜翠庄重振旗鼓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不是平时的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平时的你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用别人说  早就自顾自地把事情搅得一团糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后硬是带来一种乐观向上的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那样的你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变的不是喜翠庄  而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在大厅里接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认他们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要忘了问早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  要添粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  这个煮菜相当讲究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到自助餐里都能吃到那么棒的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用符合时节的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合上独到的精湛手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都说好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐全都变成自助式的了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的  就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是以前那种悠闲的气氛更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  这样也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然还是间隔大些比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是再往左边点好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我打算用当地画家的作品把这里布置成画廊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也可以带来一笔可观的收入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变的  喜翠庄会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你也…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄会变…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是变了  我最喜欢的喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有雪洞祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想让阿孝看看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  想让朋友看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再接待客人了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这间房可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让他看看喜翠庄是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  让他作为你的朋友留宿在这里便好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体啊情绪啊什么的还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老板娘怎么会那么好心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你重要的朋友对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来  喂——  民子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  彻先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到民子公主的睡相了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个彻是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…呐  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}别来跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在跟你怄气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绪花你站在老板娘那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学她喜欢绪花的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不那么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤底熬得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就去看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  把蔬菜给洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些结束之后就去处理鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都如彻先生所说  能做一位厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…  我之所以执着于这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有彻先生在  有莲先生在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大家在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种奇怪的东西怎么能拿得出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}我说  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碗配菜怎么还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人已经开始抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要换掉配菜 麻烦的可是我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你居然把错推到我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么  两位到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你来厨房抱怨之前  就不能想想自己能干些什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是争吵的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你说什么！别把厨房的问题推给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻必须齐心合力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}看你像块豆腐一样禁不住事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你懂什么这叫敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁的心灵才是最珍贵的你不懂么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保护喜翠庄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄…现在是重要关头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  告个别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这是个能让客人高兴的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起努力  连我也一起感觉到很幸福的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在喜翠庄却不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都只在意老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是已经知道老板娘真正的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我最喜欢的喜翠庄  是老板娘一手创造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想勉强别人去附和她的梦想么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她自己是能够奔跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有自己的梦想  不能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要能够去追随那些有着梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是他们的梦想了  这样的人也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要正式开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定许愿板上要写什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喜翠庄的人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给他们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…因为一直手忙脚乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～我说  绪花你是不是被无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名我去帮你催催
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}不等你～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}我说结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到祭典了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游客们从各地赶来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人是从东京来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…因为打扮的这么艳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  好痛  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  在这重要关头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向协会求救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家也去问过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是雪洞祭前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪洞祭前早餐和服务都要按以往的方式去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和老板娘约好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和老板娘认错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个做法的话一定还有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  给我老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还怎么能老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就输给老板娘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给…老板娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要分输赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起让客人开心  赢过老板娘更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赢的话喜翠庄就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的喜翠庄不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我喜欢的喜翠庄还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到能释放自我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的各位都是同一个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同一个心情  却又不知为何背道而驰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄已经是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  虚幻之城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说一下大家的心声…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做女服务员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能弥补巴的缺口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天两夜  大人一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐现在预约已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  和绪花一个房间好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我住的话  工作我也能帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里那么大声的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这么忙前台却一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  真的要帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老板娘…还让姐姐来帮忙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有个人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保护喜翠庄吗  Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  到了雪洞祭当天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子  现在就去月之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  忙不过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让姐姐去？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  月之间是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣的尺寸  把M换成L
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  今天我是女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好发出指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称呼错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该是老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请多关照了  翠女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  渍菜拼盘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下装饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是波之间 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  这边交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脚打扫还是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会场那边拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是鹤之间  鹤之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点摇摇晃晃而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆生意客人最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只能排第二第三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呀  我却对此乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回到你的工作岗位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之间还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  天妇罗炸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之间的我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在这里努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和老板娘一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}明白了  寿之间是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都用完餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了大家  我们渡过了难关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去参加雪洞祭
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你  最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}如果能被原谅的话  希望能再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的…
